# Reason for including .env in this repository

# This project includes the `.env` file intentionally for development and evaluation purposes.

# - The application depends on an external Aiven PostgreSQL database.
# - Including the environment configuration ensures the project can be run immediately without additional setup.
# - This is meant to simplify onboarding, testing, and demonstration of the system.

# Note:
# - These credentials are for development/demo use only.
# - They can be rotated or revoked at any time.
# - In a production setup, environment variables would NOT be committed and would be managed securely.


